
Setup test:
On gateway:    
 tcpdump -i eth1 'icmp or (tcp and dst port 8080) or (udp and dst port 53)' and src host 192.168.101.10 and dst host 192.168.201.11 -w /tmp/test.pcap

On attacker:
┌──(kali㉿kali)-[~]
└─$ ping 192.168.201.11 -c1
